snippet.title: Remnant: From the Ashes trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description:
Remnant: From the Ashes is a spooky co-op survival shooter from Perfect World and the makers of Darksiders 3, and it features some really cool looking monsters.

Find out more here: https://www.pcgamer.com/remnant-from-the-ashes-trailer-pc-gaming-show/
